			>
			<DIV>listen:&nbsp; i have been a very hardcore pvper for a very long time.&nbsp; i only play video games for their pvp, i.e. diablo, eq red servers, first person shooters, etc.&nbsp; all of my friends in games are also pvpers, and i consider myself very versed in the art of killing other players, for many years, so what i am about to say is not unfounded and needs to be said.&nbsp; PEOPLE WILL EXPLOIT THIS SYSTEM, as they have exploited every other system on every other game since the very first 2400kbps modem was ever available to purchase.&nbsp; people such as myself ONLY PLAY THESE GAMES to give other people a hard time, anyone with the notion that this system will be unexploitable needs to squash that right now.&nbsp; of course friends of bounty targets will kill them and the two of them will split the plat, THATS A FREAKIN' GIVEN.&nbsp;&nbsp;it will happen, accept it, embrace it, LOVE IT!!!!&nbsp; anyway...</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>although this is a definite, i still feel this will be a great addition to the game.&nbsp; people on blue servers already have the option to engage in pvp via the discord priest and /dueling...&nbsp; it's about damn time the red servers got a little bounce in their step, something to differentiate them even more from the wussie serv... er ahem.. excuse me... blue servers.&nbsp; but you must also take into account that this opens up TONS of doors.&nbsp; for example, being KOS now officially means something.&nbsp; pull someone in a good guild's strings the wrong way, and they'll continue to place bounties on you until you quit the freakin' character.&nbsp; its a good way to make money, if you have a twink pk already ( and i have a twink pk ranger, how convenient /grin ), among other things.&nbsp; despite the down sides, i feel this is going to be a great addition to life.&nbsp; i mean everquest...&nbsp; did i say life?&nbsp; scary...</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>in summation, be prepared for the exploitation, mark my words it will happen.&nbsp; cry me a river.&nbsp; hell if i have the chance to have my friend kill me and we split some plat, ill take it.&nbsp; you'd have to be a fool not too.&nbsp; hopefully, as i've read in some of the posts already, sony will make a few hardcore penalties for having a bounty claimed on your head, which will hopefully deter exploitation.&nbsp; all in all, it better really happen.&nbsp; if this is smoke being blown up my hooha...&nbsp; ill pk you all.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
